# Agent Systems Control Plane

- This repository can both scaffold new agent systems and analyze existing codebases.
- If the user provides a local repo path, map the repository into slices before implementation.
- Keep durable knowledge in markdown and generated artifacts.
- Prefer narrow, path-bounded tasks that can be delegated to mini-agents.
- Treat root docs and generated workspaces as first-class interfaces for external coding agents.
